{"baseRefName":"main","body":"## Summary\n\n- Require signed and notarized macOS release artifacts, build both macOS x64 and arm64 DMGs, and block unsigned macOS uploads with a clear missing-secrets error.\n- Smoke-test Linux, macOS, and Windows release artifacts on their target runners before upload, including DMG mount/copy/Gatekeeper assessment and Windows silent installer validation.\n- Add stable release artifact names, direct latest-download docs, a React GitHub Pages download site with language/theme/OS detection, and a fallback OS chooser.\n- Add the issue #6 case study with captured issue/PR/template data, reproduction evidence, screenshots, and the related upstream report: https://github.com/deep-foundation/sdk/issues/20.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `bash scripts/check-mjs-syntax.sh`\n- `bash scripts/check-file-line-limits.sh`\n- `npm run build:renderer`\n- `npm run build:site`\n- `npm run check`\n- `npm test`\n- `npx --yes -p secretlint -p @secretlint/secretlint-rule-preset-recommend secretlint \"**/*\"`\n- Playwright MCP desktop and mobile render checks for `site/dist`\n- Pre-commit `lint-staged`\n\n## Screenshots\n\n![Pages desktop](https://github.com/konard/vk-bot-desktop/blob/issue-6-4b296eea2cf6/docs/screenshots/issue-6-pages-desktop.png?raw=true)\n\n![Pages mobile](https://github.com/konard/vk-bot-desktop/blob/issue-6-4b296eea2cf6/docs/screenshots/issue-6-pages-mobile.png?raw=true)\n\n## Release Setup Required\n\nThe macOS release job now requires these repository secrets before publishing macOS artifacts: `MAC_CSC_LINK`, `MAC_CSC_KEY_PASSWORD`, `APPLE_API_KEY`, `APPLE_API_KEY_ID`, and `APPLE_API_ISSUER`.\n\n\nFixes #6","files":[{"path":".changeset/signed-desktop-downloads.md","additions":5,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":".github/workflows/electron-release.yml","additions":158,"deletions":3,"changeType":"MODIFIED"},{"path":".github/workflows/pages.yml","additions":79,"deletions":0,"changeType":"ADDED"},{"path":".gitkeep","additions":1,"deleti